&lt;p&gt;Wards 106/7 is our urology &amp; gynaecology ward, it specialises in complex urological conditions, &amp; gynaecology conditions, has its own ambulatory area and clinic area. This is a fast-paced unit at UHNM, and provides a wide varied of experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our ideal candidate would have a &#39;can do&#39; attitude to join our amazing ward team. You would be prepared to learn new skills and expand your clinical knowledge to become an expert in the urology &amp; gynaecology surgery. We advocate a learning environment and all of our staff are expected to participate in the sharing of clinical expertise and knowledge to encompass all aspects of surgical patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
